# SnapMint — YouTube Scene Screenshot to PDF (v2)

## Overview

**SnapMint**: paste a YouTube URL → **smart scene detection** → **filter out "blocked" frames** where a person is blocking center content → capture clean content screenshots with timestamps → serve as a downloadable PDF.

