## Verification Plan

### Local Testing
1. `cd backend && python app.py`
2. `cd frontend && npm run dev`
3. Test with a known lecture video (e.g., a TED Talk where presenter walks around)
4. Verify filtered vs captured scenes are correctly classified

### Deployment Testing
1. Push to GitHub → Railway auto-deploys backend
2. Push frontend → Vercel auto-deploys
3. Update `CORS_ORIGINS` on Railway with Vercel URL
4. Full end-to-end test on deployed URLs
